import React from 'react'
import {Link, NavLink} from 'react-router-dom'
import Panel from './Panel'

const Navbar = () => {

  const baseClass = 'text-white px-10'
  const activeClass =
    'border l-4 rounded text-white border-blue-500 font-bold px-10'
  return (
    <Panel className="sticky top-0 flex justify-center item-start">
      <NavLink
        to="/"
        className={({isActive}) =>
          isActive ? activeClass : baseClass
        }
      >
        Home
      </NavLink>

      <NavLink
        to="/accordion"
        className={({isActive}) => (isActive ? activeClass : baseClass)}
      >
        About Me
      </NavLink>

      <NavLink
        to="/dropdown"
        className={({isActive}) => (isActive ? activeClass : baseClass)}
      >
        Projects
      </NavLink>
    </Panel>
  )
}

export default Navbar
